movieData.movieTitle: I Could Never Be Your Woman
movieData.movieComments: Youtube has a lot of these DVD rom coms on their movie section and most of them aren't great. Paul Rudd is in this and I feel like they just had him show up and told him to improv everything. It's otherwise a forgettable movie.

I'm not sure how I feel about sydney sweeney as an actress she kind of reminds me of kristen stewart. She has a very monotone voice. The movies plot and twist was good. Definitely different than the nanny diaries. The ending definitely dragged on (spoilers) but it could've just ended with andrew getting locked in the room. Everything after that was pretty much just filler except the last 2-3lines of the movie before the credits which was great.
